The '''''Barkham Burroughs' Encyclopaedia of Astounding Facts and Useful Information''''' was an [[encyclopaedia]] published by Barkham Burroughs in 1889.<ref>[http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13304185-barkham-burroughs-encyclopedia-astound]</ref>

== Content ==

The book provides many old and interesting home remedies and recipes that anyone can try at their homes.<ref>[http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13304185-barkham-burroughs-encyclopedia-astound]</ref>

The book is currently out of copyright and is therefore available free of cost in the [[United States]].

The book has been digitized by [[Project Gutenberg]] and is now easily available on the internet.

==  Reception ==

The book has generally received very positive reviews from readers and critics.<ref>[http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13304185-barkham-burroughs-encyclopedia-astound]</ref>

