== File format support ==
''See [[Comparison of e-book formats]] for details on the file formats.''

The most notable formats are:
* [[EPUB|.epub]] is a free and open e-book standard used by most e-readers.
* [[Amazon Kindle#Content support|.azw]] is Amazon's proprietary e-book file format used in Kindles.

